p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-fZekov0n38p16zJzIaCBWA">Thu dạ hoài ngâm - 秋夜懷吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%89nh-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-d%E1%BA%ABn-ng%C3%A2n-b%C3%ACnh/poem-fEvivJabPd3uwuqTNX3otg">Tỉnh để dẫn ngân bình - 井底引銀瓶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BA%A3o-H%E1%BA%A3o-thi/poem-ZLgiAlRmZdlWf7MkDKd1sg">Trương Hảo Hảo thi - 張好好詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
